  "description": "<p>An ultralight and comfortable option for sport or alpine climbing. It's tricked out with a host of thoughtful features and uses Fuseframe construction to produce a very slim, clean, lightweight design. Dyneema belay loop and tie-in points are designed to resist wear and provide seasons of use.</p><ul><li>Fuseframe construction distributes weight over the structure and minimizes pressure points</li><li>Fused fabric and foam layers have no crossing seams to create friction zones</li><li>TPU reinforcements on lower leg loops add durability</li><li>DoubleBack aluminum HD buckle has a slim, rounded design that offers good grip and fluid glide on the waist webbing</li><li>Fitted elastic leg loops offer freedom of movement</li><li>4 equipment loops: rigid in front are angled to push gear forward for easy access and flexible in the rear to avoid creating pressure points with a backpack</li><li>Compatible with Caritool Evo</li><li>Reinforced tie-in points</li></ul>",
